### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Grafana webhook：portfolio 支付回调超时告警入站
POST http://localhost:8080/api/alerts/grafana
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alerts": [
    {
      "fingerprint": "payment-alert-demo-001",
      "startsAt": "2026-07-04T00:00:00Z",
      "labels": {
        "alertname": "支付回调超时",
        "service": "payment-service",
        "endpoint": "/api/payment/callback",
        "trace_id": "trace-payment-timeout-001",
        "exception_type": "TimeoutError",
        "severity": "P1",
        "error_rate": "0.082",
        "p95_latency": "3200",
        "qps": "1260",
        "affected_requests": "238"
      },
      "annotations": {
        "summary": "portfolio 支付回调链路错误率和延迟同时升高",
        "description": "5 分钟窗口内 payment-service callback timeout spike"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Alertmanager webhook：同一类告警的另一种入站格式
POST http://localhost:8080/api/alerts/alertmanager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alerts": [
    {
      "fingerprint": "payment-alert-demo-002",
      "startsAt": "2026-07-04T00:02:00Z",
      "labels": {
        "alertname": "支付回调超时",
        "service": "payment-service",
        "endpoint": "/api/payment/callback",
        "trace_id": "trace-payment-timeout-002",
        "exception_type": "TimeoutError",
        "severity": "P1"
      },
      "annotations": {
        "summary": "portfolio 支付回调超时告警",
        "error_rate": "0.082",
        "p95_latency": "3200",
        "qps": "1260",
        "affected_requests": "238"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### 本地兼容 demo：触发支付回调超时样例故障
POST http://localhost:8080/api/demo/faults/payment-timeout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoCreateIncident": true
}

### 创建支付回调超时 Incident
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "payment-service 支付回调超时",
  "serviceName": "payment-service",
  "endpoint": "/api/payment/callback",
  "source": "DEMO",
  "traceId": "trace-payment-timeout-001",
  "exceptionType": "TimeoutError",
  "summary": "5 分钟内 500 错误率升高，p95 延迟升至 3200ms"
}

### 启动 Workflow
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/start-workflow
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询 Workflow 节点
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/1/nodes

### 查询 Incident 列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents

### 查询 Incident 详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1

### 查询 Workflow 实例
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/1

### 查询处置方案
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/actions

### 查询 MCP / LLM 工具调用审计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/1/tool-calls

### 记录处置结果
POST http://localhost:8080/api/actions/1/record-result
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "executor": "sre-demo",
  "resultDetail": "已在线下通过值班系统开启延迟重试，本系统只记录处理结果"
}

### 查询 Incident 指标快照
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/metrics

### 生成复盘
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/generate-postmortem
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询复盘
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/postmortem

### 关闭 Incident
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "closedBy": "demo-user",
  "comment": "指标恢复，复盘已生成"
}
